thread.title: Shireen Rout
thread.title_full: PACK & SEND Australia reviewed by Shireen Rout

author: Shireen Rout
title: Shireen Rout
text: I booked a couple of boxes for postage online and took the boxes to the store at Campbelltown for delivery. The staff were professional and friendly. The whole process was easy and the staff wrapped up the boxes for me in plastic to be delivered. My boxes arrived to their destination the next day. Thankyou, very happy with the service.
